AboutMe.title: Who am I?
AboutMe.description:
Hello! My name is Jônatas.
I am a front/backend developer who enjoys playing programming.
I've made some interesting projects, like Xurumin, a Discord bot with the main purpose of entertaining its users (used by over 1400 guilds and 120k users).
